Source: dbt2-extensions
Section: database
Priority: optional
Maintainer: Ruohang Feng <rh@vonng.com>
Build-Depends: debhelper-compat (= 13), postgresql-all (>= 217~)
Standards-Version: 4.6.2
Rules-Requires-Root: no
Homepage: https://github.com/osdldbt/dbt2

Package: postgresql-PGVERSION-dbt2
Architecture: any
Provides: postgresql-dbt2
Depends: ${postgresql:Depends}, ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}
Description: DBT-2 PostgreSQL stored functions for PostgreSQL PGVERSION
 This package contains the C stored functions used by the DBT-2 benchmark.
 The separate benchmark driver, schemas, and data-generation toolchain are not
 included.
